process help=*
PARM PAN TYPE=STRING
PARM INP TYPE=STRING COUNT=(2:20)
PARM OUT TYPE=STRING COUNT=(2:20)

END-PROC
.TITLE
brovey - apply Brovey Transform to pan sharpen msi
.HELP
PURPOSE:

The input is a pan image plus n multi-spectral images, all of the same
nl, ns. It is assumed that the 2-20 msi images have been scaled up to
the pan resolution. There are n output images, i.e. the pan-sharpened
msi.

The Brovey transform is:

bandN = pan * bandN / (band1 + band2 + band3 + ... + bandM)

EXECUTION:

Example

brovey PAN inp=(B1,B2,B3,B4,B5) out=(S1,S2,S3,S4,S5)
                               
